Prime 5.35'Acre Commercial Parcel on HWY 70 " Thatcher, AZ Position your business for success on this exceptional 5.35'acre commercial property fronting the highly traveled Highway 70 corridor in Thatcher. Located in one of the area's most sought'after commercial zones, this parcel offers outstanding visibility, strong daily traffic flow, and direct access for customers, clients, and deliveries.

This 9.71 acres is in a great location, very close to Thatcher City ball fields, park, pickleball, and walking and bike paths. Beautiful sunsets and views of Mt. Graham can be enjoyed here. Additionally, a natural spring is located on the northwest side of the property, which flows well, particularly during the monsoon season. Bring your horses and build on this centrally located property. Electric service is available on the lot line, while water and sewer services are situated on Reay Lane, and a septic system is also available.
